@startuml
hide empty description

'state Monolith
state "Monolith (Co-Located Presentation, Business Logic, Persistence)" as Monolith
state "Distributed Presentation" as DistributedPresentation
state "Remote User Interface" as RemoteUI

Monolith --> DistributedPresentation : (A) Introduce thin \napplication frontend\n(thin client, server-side rendering)
Monolith --> RemoteUI : (B) Introduce rich \napplication frontend \n(remote user interface, client-side rendering)

DistributedPresentation --> RemoteUI : (C) Switch to \nremote user interface
RemoteUI --> DistributedPresentation : (D) Switch to \ndistributed presentation

DistributedPresentation -[dashed]-> Monolith : (E) Return to \nmonolith
RemoteUI -[dashed]-> Monolith : (E) Return to \nmonolith
@enduml